      </div>
      <div class="collab-box">
        <div class="collab-title">Collaboration Opportunity</div>
        <p>Xpensease reads UPI/bank SMS and tracks spend. Razorpay powers millions of UPI transactions daily. A payment link API integration would let Xpensease users settle Group Splits with one tap — no manual app-switching. Razorpay gains deeper stickiness in a daily-use finance audience. Pitch as a scoped 2-week pilot.</p>
      </div>
