        <p>Slice users carry credit and split expenses constantly. Xpensease's Single Split and PayAlert features solve exactly the pain point — "who owes me for last month's trip?" A bundled feature placement or co-branded campus campaign targeting college hostels would give Slice a stickiness boost while bringing Xpensease its core demographic.</p>
