        <p>A user who tracks every rupee with Xpensease is a high-intent investor — exactly who Groww wants. Propose a "Save what you don't spend" CTA inside Xpensease's budget summary screen that deep-links to Groww's SIP onboarding. Revenue model: affiliate/referral per signup. This creates a full financial flywheel: spend awareness → savings → investment.</p>
